Installation notes for SpamCruncher

Basically, SpamCruncher can just be started on any computer running Perl5. (tested with 5.6.1)
Just unpack the download and run the script. But please note the following prerequisites:

You need to have the following perl-modules installed to run SpamCruncher:

Mail::Spamassassin
Mail::IMAPclient
Mail::POP3client
Mail::Sendmail
Getopt:Std
Term::ReadKey
IO::File

Please see the CPAN for downloading purposes. (www.cpan.org)
